name: Ceramiaceae along the East-African coast sampled between 1985 and 1997
description: This dataset contains a list of species of Ceramiaceaepresent at the coast ofKenya,Tanzania and the Seychelles sampledbetween 1985 and 1997.Mostspecimens have been collected by wadingorsnorkeling. The data were digitized by VLIZ from the original report: Roels, T. (1998).Taxonomisch-morfologische studie van enkel genera van de Ceramiaceaelangs de Oost-Afrikaanse kust = Taxonomic-morphological study of a few generaof the Ceramiaceae along the East-African coast. MScThesis. Rijksuniversiteit Gent. Faculteit Wetenschappen: Gent. 65, 48 platen, appendices pp.
